#~ "<p>Kate has a built-in terminal emulator, just click on "
#~ "<strong>\"Terminal\"</strong> at\n"
#~ "the bottom to show or hide it as you desire.</p>\n"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<html><p align=\"left\">Kate には組み込みのターミナルエミュレータが備わっ"
